{
  "stem": "23438.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We lived there for about two years.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that was my first and only contact with a really Jewish world in Warsaw, until the war.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then when things improved, we moved into Mokotowska, number three.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We had a lovely flat there, three room, on the ground floor, in the back part of the flat.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So we didn't face the street, but the yard.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there we loved living.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was almost the end of this part of town.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And next to us was vacant-- vacant land that was used sometimes as a horse-racing ground.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That was later, during the war, converted into little vegetable gardens.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this part was really nice, except for the character that was stopping me in the street there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because that's where it had happened to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I give a lot of thought to those early-- early years of mine.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know whether my parents were right, bringing us up this way.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I found it that maybe if we were enlightened as to our origins, as to our belonging, maybe it wouldn't be such a shock to find out what we were, what Hitler wanted-- wanted us to be.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Having a Jewish grandmother and grandfather, even if they were converted, still made us Jewish.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was nothing to alter that fact.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't think I was really interested in anything like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we-- we-- it was not a topic we talked about at home.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I did not actually meet anti-Semitism at school, either of the schools I went to.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that these were the only instances.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I don't think it was ever a topic spoken about at home, to any extent.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very much so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very much so.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
